Package: usearchlite
Title: Local Vector Search with USearch (Lite)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Alejandro", "JimÃ©nez Rico", email = "aljrico@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A lightweight local vector index for approximate nearest neighbor
    (ANN) search using the vendored USearch library. Provides a simple interface
    for adding vectors, searching for nearest neighbors, and persisting indexes
    to disk. Metadata filtering is performed in R on the candidate set returned
    by the C++ layer.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/aljrico/usearchlite
BugReports: https://github.com/aljrico/usearchlite/issues
